<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.4">
<l>ārē yulakat tāṟṟuvā rāyar pāṭi kavarntuṇṇuṅ</l>
<l>kārē ṟuḻakka vuḻakkuṇṭu taḷarntum muṟintuṅ kiṭappēṉai</l>
<l>ārā vamuta maṉaiyāṉṟa ṉamuta vāyi lūṟiya</l>
<l>nīrtāṉ koṇarntu pularāmē parukki yiḷaippai nīkkirē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will console me, who have grown faint and broken having been devastated</l>
<l>As the black Bull who eats by stealing from the [whole] Gokula trampled [on my heart]?</l>
<l>Bring the water that sprung from the nectar[-like] mouth of He</l>
<l rend="indent">who is like nectar that does not sate,</l>
<l>have [me] drink [it] so that [my body] does not dry up, and [thus] remove [my] weariness!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
